ygData.messageBody:
Grats on 52!

I read a post on Fires of Heaven noos board that two of them hit 56 and
heard rumor that they are being power played 24/7. They want to be the
first to hit 60 and do it a.s.a.p. And playing 24 hours a day for exp will
definitely get you there.

Sylly

p.s. also saw some equilizer/stratics posts from miriana's guild on phat
l3wt's they hauled in. one was the new mask with illusion iskar effect. i
think stats were the same as mask of deceiver but the illusion is Iskar.
WTG LoD!
